NAME
     9x more scum & rats than rio. Just say NEIN.

DESCRIPTION
     9x is a scummy X11 window manager. A rat infested rio rip-off.  It
     provides far more than you bargained for.  Do 9 things and do them
     poorly.

OPTIONS
     -v  Erase computer. Weep.

MOUSE
   Run Button
     Hover        Launch.
   Launcher
     Button 1     Launch.
     Button 3     Sweep.
   Window Tabs
     Hover        Focus.
     Button 1     Maximize.
     Button 2     Delete.
     Button 3     Re-Sweep.
   Desktop Buttons
     Button 1     Switch to Desktop.
     Button 2     Window to Desktop.
     Button 3     Follow Window to Desktop.
   Window Borders
     Button 1     Resize.
     Button 2     Delete.
     Button 3     Move.
     Doubleclick  Tile.
   Battery/Clock
     B1/2/3       Sweep.
     B4/5         Scroll Desktops.
   Root Window
     B1/2/3       Sweep.
     B4/5         Scroll Desktops.
   Root Edges & Corners
     Edgesnapping

CUSTOMIZATION
     Read the goddamn src(1) you filthy heathen.

